---
// src/pages/en/datenschutz.astro
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | Nutritionist Visit Card" lang="ru">
  <main class="bg-stone-50 py-20 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto bg-white p-8 md:p-12 shadow-sm border border-stone-100 rounded-2xl">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-2 text-center uppercase tracking-tight">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-center text-stone-400 text-xs mb-8 uppercase tracking-widest">(Datenschutzerklärung)</p>

      <div class="prose prose-stone prose-sm max-w-none text-stone-700 leading-relaxed space-y-8">
        
        <div class="bg-amber-50 border-l-4 border-amber-200 p-4 text-amber-800 text-xs italic">
          Disclaimer: This is a translation of the legally binding German "Datenschutzerklärung". In case of any discrepancies, the German version shall prevail.
        </div>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-4 border-b pb-2">1. An Overview of Data Protection</h2>
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-2 text-stone-800">General Information</h3>
          <p>The following notes provide a simple overview of what happens to your personal data when you visit this website. Personal data is any data that can be used to identify you personally.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-4 border-b pb-2">2. Hosting and Server Log Files</h2>
          <p>Our website is hosted on external servers (Vercel). When you visit our site, the server automatically collects and stores information in so-called server log files, which your browser automatically transmits to us:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc ml-5 space-y-1">
            <li>Browser type and browser version</li>
            <li>Operating system used</li>
            <li>Referrer URL</li>
            <li>Host name of the accessing computer</li>
            <li>Time of the server request</li>
            <li>IP address</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-2 text-xs italic">The basis for data processing is Art. 6 para. 1 lit. f GDPR, which permits the processing of data to fulfill a contract or for measures prior to a contract.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-4 border-b pb-2">3. Social Media & Communication</h2>
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-1 text-stone-800 text-base">LinkedIn</h3>
          <p>Our website uses functions of the LinkedIn network. If you click on a LinkedIn link, a connection to LinkedIn's servers is established. LinkedIn will be informed that you have visited our website with your IP address.</p>
          
          <h3 class="font-bold mt-4 mb-1 text-stone-800 text-base">WhatsApp</h3>
          <p>For fast communication, we use WhatsApp. The provider is WhatsApp Ireland Limited. Communication is end-to-end encrypted, however, WhatsApp may collect metadata (time, sender, recipient).</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-4 border-b pb-2">4. Plugins and Tools</h2>
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-1 text-stone-800 text-base">Google Web Fonts</h3>
          <p>This site uses web fonts provided by Google for the uniform display of fonts. When you call up a page, your browser loads the required web fonts into your browser cache to display texts and fonts correctly. For this purpose, the browser you use must connect to Google's servers, which means Google becomes aware that our website was accessed via your IP address.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-4 border-b pb-2">5. Your Rights as a Data Subject</h2>
          <p>You have the right at any time to receive information free of charge about the origin, recipient, and purpose of your stored personal data. You also have a right to request the correction or deletion of this data. If you have given your consent to data processing, you can revoke this consent at any time for the future.</p>
        </section>

      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-stone-100 text-center">
        <a href="/ru" class="text-green-600 font-bold hover:text-green-700 transition">← Back to Homepage</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>